# S07: Testing & Reliability

## Objective
Demonstrate production engineering quality with comprehensive test coverage.

## Tasks
- [ ] S07-T01-VitestSetup.pd — Setup Vitest + React Testing Library
- [ ] S07-T02-PlaywrightSetup.pd — Setup Playwright E2E
- [ ] S07-T03-MSWSetup.pd — Setup Mock Service Worker for API mocking
- [ ] S07-T04-UnitTests.pd — Unit tests: telemetry parsing, binary decoding, performance manager
- [ ] S07-T05-ComponentTests.pd — Component tests: radar, graphs, touch controls
- [ ] S07-T06-IntegrationTests.pd — Integration: WebSocket reconnect, stream switching, HUD rendering
- [ ] S07-T07-PerformanceTests.pd — Performance regression + memory leak tests
- [ ] S07-T08-StressTests.pd — Stress tests for telemetry bursts

## Invariants
- Test files colocated with source (feature/component/__tests__/)
- No snapshot tests — prefer behavioral assertions
- Performance tests: 30 FPS minimum maintained under load
- MSW for all API/WebSocket mocking in tests
